    .about-me
      p 'O Rows' is an idea of an app.
      p It allows teams to curate organized knowledge-bases rather than just spreadsheets.
      p You can define data schemas which can be nested with relationships.
      p You can add rich fields such as images, files, audio clips, markdown text. You can even set validations and calculated fields.
      p You can share only parts of data with other users, or have it view-only with comments and accept suggestions. You can even set permissions at a row and field level. '(O_o) rows!'
      p If you make a mistake, or someone adds bad data, you can always audit and fix it. Version history is automatically saved.
      p You can customize rows to look like tiles, or tree grids, or kanban boards. You can be customize rows with custom html and css. You can even build a website out of it if you want!
      p You can create management systems for projects, customers, library books, schedules, inventory e.t.c. If you have structured data, ORows is your tool!
      p Send an email to hello@orows.com if you are interested.
